Package com.oopsipushedtomain

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.oopsipushedtomain.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Event extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an event within the application. This class is used to model events, including their details such as title, start and end times, description, location, poster URL, QR code data, and attendee limit. It implements Serializable to allow event instances to be passed between activities or components.

Outstanding issues: None known at this time.
